collectionMetadata.name: Rainfall - Monthly Number of Rain Days
collectionMetadata.description: The number of rain days (day with rainfall amount of 0.2mm or more) in a month recorded at the Changi Climate Station.

datasetMetadata.name: Rainfall - Monthly Number of Rain Days
datasetMetadata.description: Number of rain days per month at the Changi Climate Station. A day is considered to have "rained" if the total rainfall for that day is 0.2mm or more.
